nhc_headline: ...DISTURBANCE EXPECTED STRENGTHEN AND BRING SIGNIFICANT WINDS AND RAIN TO PORTIONS OF SOUTHERN MEXICO...
summary: ...DISTURBANCE EXPECTED STRENGTHEN AND BRING SIGNIFICANT WINDS AND RAIN TO PORTIONS OF SOUTHERN MEXICO... As of 3:00 PM CST Mon Jun 16 the center of Five-E was located near 10.6, -91.7 with movement WNW at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 1009 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 35 mph.
